          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1Preheat waffle iron and grease with cooking spray."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "ccedfc22-7360-4fc7-a344-b16f5501f292",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2Combine all of the ingredients, except for the sour cream, in a large mixing bowl; mix and stir until thoroughly incorporated."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "0fceeb57-2480-42b5-9c48-596ce739ce07",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3If you want smaller waffles, scoop out about 1/3 cup of the batter and form into a patty. For bigger waffles, use 1/2 cup of the batter. For a perfect serving size, use 2 ounces of the batter per waffle."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "8d843931-2f9e-4a4e-8979-12ec4e75a461",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "4Transfer to preheated waffle iron and close; cook for 3 to 4 minutes, or until cooked through and browned on top. Cooking time will depend on the size of the waffles."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "dc3c3922-f36c-4c1b-9406-b74882c93c51",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "5Remove from waffle iron, top with a sprinkle of cheese (optional) and set aside."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "afdf892f-db98-4338-9126-fabe3e4a17db",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "6Repeat with the remaining batter."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "de1682ef-5d6e-4e93-818e-afc8c7ac8cbc",
          "input_qty": null,
